{ "Unheard melodies" }
1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 d6 6. Bc4 Qb6 7. Nde2 (7. Nxc6 bxc6 8. O-O g6 9. Qe1 $14 { Modern theory goes on from here: } { Ivanchuk, V. - Maghsoodloo, Parham, 1/2-1/2, 32nd Leon GM 2019, https://lichess.org/Iugnjhxk } { [%cal Ge4e5] }) 7... e6 8. O-O Be7 9. Bb3 O-O 10. Kh1 { [%cal Gf2f4,Gf4f5] } (10. Be3 Qc7 11. f4 Ng4!) 10... Na5 11. Bg5 Qc5 12. f4 (12. Be3?! Qc7 $10 { [%cal Ga5c4] }) 12... b5 13. Ng3 b4?! (13... Nxb3 14. axb3 Bb7 15. Nh5 Kh8 $15) 14. e5!? dxe5 (14... Nxb3?? 15. exf6 gxf6 (15... Bxf6 16. Nce4 $18) 16. Bh6 $18 { [%cal Gd1g4,Gg4g8] }) (14... bxc3?? 15. exf6 gxf6 16. Bh6 Kh8 17. Bxf8 Bxf8 18. bxc3 $16) 15. Bxf6 gxf6? (15... bxc3! 16. Ne4 Qb4 17. Qg4 Bxf6 18. Nxf6+ Kh8 19. Qh4 h6 20. Ng4 $10 { but white does still maintain a possible attack. }) 16. Nce4! Qd4? (16... Qc7 { Benko considered this move for a long time - but it's lost in all but one line, in which case black is worse anyway in an endgame. } 17. Nh5 Kh8! (17... f5 18. Nhf6+! Kg7 19. Qh5! Bxf6 (19... h6?? 20. Rf3 Rh8 21. Rg3+ Kf8 22. Qxh6+ Rxh6 23. Rg8#) (19... Rh8?? 20. Qg5+ Kf8 21. Qh6#) 20. Nxf6 h6 21. Rf3! Kxf6?? (21... Rh8 22. Ne8+!! Rxe8 23. Rg3+ Kf8 24. Qxh6+ Ke7 25. Qh4+ Kd6 $18 (25... Kf8 26. Rh3 Qd8 27. Qh6+ Ke7 28. Qg5+ $18 { [%cal Ge7f8,Gh3h8,Re7d7,Ra1d1,Bf7f6,Bh3h7] })) 22. Qh4+ Kg7 23. Rg3+ Kh7 24. Rh3 $18 { [%cal Gh4h6] }) 18. Nexf6 Qd8 19. fxe5 Qxd1 20. Raxd1 Nxb3 21. cxb3 $14 { Black is out of the woods here, but in a slightly worse position. }) 17. Qh5 Nxb3 (17... Kh8 18. Qh6 Rg8 (18... Bb7 19. Nxf6 { [%cal Gh6h7] } 19... Bxf6 20. Qxf6+ Kg8 21. Nh5 $18 { [%cal Gf6g7] }) 19. Nxf6 Bxf6 20. Qxf6+ Rg7 21. Nh5 $18 { [%cal Gf6g7] }) (17... exf4 18. Nf5!! exf5 19. Rxf4! { And the threat of Rh4 forced black to give up the queen: } 19... fxe4?? (19... Qxe4 20. Rxe4 fxe4 21. Qxa5 $18) 20. Rh4 $18) 18. Qh6!! exf4 (18... f5 19. Ng5 Bxg5 20. Qxg5+ Kh8 21. Qf6+ Kg8 22. Rad1! Qxb2 (22... Nd2 23. Rxd2 Qxd2 24. Nh5 $18) 23. Nh5 $18) 19. Nh5 f5 20. Rad1! Qe5 (20... Qxb2?? 21. c3!) 21. Nef6+ Bxf6 22. Nxf6+ Qxf6 23. Qxf6 Nc5 24. Qg5+ Kh8 25. Qe7 { [%cal Ge7c5,Ge7f8] } 25... Ba6 26. Qxc5 Bxf1 27. Rxf1 $18 { 1-0 Black resigns. } { Black resigned rather than deal with this completely lost rook vs queen position. } 1-0


