{ "Old wine in a new bottle" }
1. e4 e5 2. f4 exf4 3. Nf3 g5 (3... d6 { The Fischer defense - "discovered" after this game }) 4. h4 g4 5. Ne5 Nf6 6. d4 (6. Bc4 d5 7. exd5 Bg7) (6. Nxg4 Nxe4 7. d3 Ng3 8. Bxf4 Nxh1 9. Qe2+ Qe7 10. Nf6+ Kd8 11. Bxc7+ Kxc7 12. Nd5+ Kd8 13. Nxe7 Bxe7 $15 { Morphy - Anderssen, 1858 }) 6... d6 7. Nd3 Nxe4 8. Bxf4 Bg7 9. Nc3? (9. c3 O-O 10. Nd2 Re8 11. Nxe4 Rxe4+ 12. Be2 g3 13. Bxg3 Bg4 14. Nf4 Qe7 15. Kf2 Bxe2 16. Nxe2 Nd7 17. Nf4 $17) 9... Nxc3 10. bxc3 c5 11. Be2 (11. Qe2+ Be6 12. d5?? Bxc3+ $19) 11... cxd4 12. O-O Nc6 (12... h5? 13. Bg5 f6 14. Bc1 $14 { [%cal Gd3f4,Gf4g6,Gf4e6,Gf4d5] }) 13. Bxg4 O-O 14. Bxc8 Rxc8 15. Qg4 f5 (15... Kh8 { A safer choice, but winning a second pawn has its merits }) 16. Qg3 dxc3 17. Rae1 (17. Bxd6? Rf6 18. Bf4 Rg6 $17 { "with the initiative" }) 17... Kh8 18. Kh1?! (18. Bxd6! Rf6 (18... Rg8 19. Ne5! Qxd6?? 20. Nf7#) 19. Bf4 Rg6 20. Bg5 Qd4+ 21. Kh1 $10) 18... Rg8 (18... d5? 19. Nc5 $15 { [%cal Gc5e6,Gc5d7,Gc5b7] }) 19. Bxd6 Bf8 (19... Bd4 20. Qh2 Rg4 21. Be5+ Kg8 22. Rf4! $10) 20. Be5+ Nxe5 21. Qxe5+ Rg7 { "Now white's h pawn must fall" } 22. Rxf5 Qxh4+ 23. Kg1 Qg4 (23... Qg3 24. Qxg3 Rxg3 { Black has threats, but the endgame could still be drawn with best play. } { Zylla, Johannes - Marchisotti, Dr. Mauro, 1/2-1/2, WSTT/1/06/sf1, 2007, https://lichess.org/5ylXT1lN } { [%cal Gg3d3,Gc2d3,Gc3c2] }) 24. Rf2 Be7 25. Re4 Qg5 (25... Qd1+ 26. Re1 Qg4 27. Re4 Qd1+ 28. Kh2 Rc6 { [%cal Gc6h6] } 29. Qb8+ Rg8 30. Qe5+ Rg7 $10 { Both sides have a draw here with best play. Fischer wanted more. }) 26. Qd4! { "This powerful centralization completely paralyzes black" } 26... Rf8?? (26... Bf8 27. Ne5 (27. Qxa7 Bd6 $10 { [%cal Gd3e5,Gd6e5] }) 27... Bc5! { The move that Fischer had missed. He was worried about Nf7+ } 28. Nf7+ Kg8 29. Nh6+ (29. Nxg5 Bxd4 30. Rxd4 Rxg5 $10) 29... Qxh6 30. Qxc5 $10) 27. Re5! Rd8 (27... Qg6 28. Rxe7 $18 { [%csl Gf8][%cal Gf2f8,Gd4h8] }) (27... Qh4 28. Rxf8+! Bxf8 29. Qxh4 $18) (27... Bf6 28. Qd6 $18 { [%cal Gd6f8,Ge5g5] }) 28. Qe4! Qh4 (28... Qg3 29. Rxe7 $18) 29. Rf4! $18 { 1-0 Black resigns. } { [%cal Ge5e7] } 1-0


