{ "Hoist with his own petard" }
1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 d6 5. O-O Bg4 6. h3 Bh5 (6... h5!? 7. Bxc6+ bxc6 8. d4 $16 { White gets the center, and the pin cannot be maintained forever. }) 7. c3 Qf6?? $146 { "Geller looked quite happy after this novelty" but it's rubbish as it does not adequately attack/defend the center. } (7... Nf6 8. Re1 Be7 9. d3 O-O 10. Nbd2 b5 11. Bb3 Na5 12. Bc2 c5 13. Nf1 { [%cal Gf1g3] } 13... Nc6 14. Ng3 Bg6 { In general, the early Bg4/Bg5 maneuvers in the Ruy Lopez don't inconvenience the opponent at all. } { [%cal Gf3h4,Gh4f5] }) 8. g4! { Capitalizing on black's lack of development! } 8... Bg6 9. d4! Bxe4 10. Nbd2 Bg6? (10... Bxf3 11. Nxf3 e4 12. Re1 d5 13. Bg5 Qd6 14. c4! $18 { White rips open the center before black can finish development. }) (10... Bd3 11. Bxc6+ bxc6 12. Re1 O-O-O 13. Re3! $18 { Smyslov, Vassily - Medina Garcia, Antonio Angel, 1-0, Tel Aviv ol (Men) fin-A, 1964, https://lichess.org/4VcKpTkc }) 11. Bxc6+ bxc6 12. dxe5 (12. Qa4!! Ne7? (12... Kd7 13. dxe5 dxe5 14. Nc4 Bd6 15. Rd1 Re8 { "White has no immediate way to exploit the exposed king" except that's completely incorrect: } 16. Rxd6+!! cxd6 17. Qb4! { [%cal Gb4b7] } 17... Rc8 18. Qb7+ Rc7 19. Nb6+ Kd8 20. Qb8+ Rc8 21. Qxc8+ $18) 13. dxe5 dxe5 14. Re1 e4 15. Nxe4 Qxf3 16. Qxc6+!! Nxc6 17. Nf6+ Kd8 18. Re8#) 12... dxe5 13. Nxe5 Bd6 (13... O-O-O 14. Qe2! { [%cal Ge2a6] } 14... Kb7 15. Nb3 { [%cal Rb3a5] } 15... Rd5 { [%cal Bd5a5] } 16. Re1 $18) 14. Nxg6 Qxg6 { "Geller took a half hour on this recapture and stopped looking happy." The obvious recapture fails: } (14... hxg6 15. Ne4! Qh4 (15... Qe5 16. Nxd6+ Qxd6 (16... cxd6?? 17. Re1 $18) 17. Re1+ Kd7 18. Bf4! Qxd1 19. Raxd1+ $18) 16. Nxd6+ cxd6 17. Qxd6 Qxh3?? 18. Re1+ $18 { [%cal Ge1e8,Gd6f8,Gd6d8] }) 15. Re1+ Kf8 (15... Ne7 16. Nc4 O-O-O 17. Qa4 $18 { [%cal Ga4a6,Ga4c6,Gc4d6,Gc4b6] }) 16. Nc4 h5! { Counterplay has to come from somewhere! } 17. Nxd6 cxd6 18. Bf4 d5?? (18... Rd8 19. Qe2 hxg4 20. hxg4 f5! { The only move in this almost zugzwang. } (20... Qh7?? 21. Bxd6+! { [%cal Ge2e8] }) 21. Rad1 Qxg4+ 22. Qxg4 fxg4 23. Re6 $16 { With perfect defense, black was escaping with a terrible endgame. }) 19. Qb3 hxg4 (19... Ne7 20. Rxe7 Kxe7 21. Qb7+ $18) (19... Nf6 20. Qb7 Re8 21. Rxe8+ Nxe8 22. Re1 Qf6 23. Qc8 $18 { [%cal Gc8e8] }) 20. Qb7! gxh3+ 21. Bg3 Rd8 22. Qb4+ $18 { 1-0 Black resigns. } { White wins both the e7 knight AND the d8 rook. } 22... Ne7 (22... Rd6?? 23. Qb8+ Rd8 24. Qxd8#) 23. Qxe7+ Kg8 24. Qxd8+ Kh7 25. Qh4+ Kg8 26. Re8# 1-0


