Gh4g5,Gd7e6] } 35. Rxf5 Rxh4 36. Rxd5+ Ke6 { [%cal Ga6f1] } 37. Rcd1 (37. Re5+ Kf6 38. Rf1+?? { [%cal Gf1f6] } 38... Kg7 39. Bxh4 { If the queen wasn't looking at f1, this variation would have been nice. }) 37... Qc4 38. Rd6+ Ke7 39. Rd7+ Kf6 (39... Kf8 40. Rd8+ Kg7 41. Be5+ f6 42. R8d7+ Kh6 43. Bxf6 { Looks scary, but... } { [%cal Gd7d8,Gd8h8] } 43... Rf4! $19) 40. Bxh4+ Qxh4 41. Rf1+ Kg5 42. Rd5+ f5 43. Rxa5 $10 { Draw agreed. } 1/2-1/2


