{ The most famous checkmate from this series. Bobby Fischer defeats his esteemed Mongolian opponent in style! }
1. Qh6 (1. hxg6?? { No mate! Black's rook on a7 can defend laterally after fxg6 } 1... fxg6) 1... Qf8 { Black needed to defend the mate on g7 } 2. Qxh7+! Kxh7 3. hxg6+ Kxg6 4. Be4# { Again showcasing the power of double checks in forcing attacks - the king has to move! } *


