{ This study will contain my personal annotations on the final chapter from IM Jeremy Silman's fantastic book "Complete Endgame Course." While most of the book is on theoretical endgames, the final chapter takes us through Silman's choice of the five greatest endgame players of all time. Throughout the annotations, Silman's words will be put "in quotes," while my personal comments will be plain text.

This won't have the same feel as other NoseKnowsAll instructive studies, as the annotations will be quite light, but I hope you get something out of it anyway.

To get the most out of this study, I strongly suggest you follow along the actual book as well! }
 *


