{ Remember that in this position, we have to play h5 in order to cut out white's kingside nonsense and ensure our bishop isn't trapped. }
4... e6?? { This thematic move in the Advanced variation doesn't pay attention to white's threat from last move. } (4... h5! { Recall how we have to stop white from further expanding on the kingside before completing development with e6. }) 5. g4! Be4 6. f3 Bg6 7. h5 $18 { The bishop is trapped. Don't let this happen to you! } *


[Event "Learn the Caro-Kann like a BOSS: Don't get greedy trap"]
[Date "2023.12.06"]
[Result "*"]
[Variant "Standard"]
