1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Nxe5 d6 4. Nf3 Nxe4 5. d4 d5 6. Bd3 Be7 7. O-O Nc6 8. c4 Nb4 9. Be2 O-O (9... dxc4 10. Bxc4 { [%csl Gd4] }) 10. a3 Nc6 11. cxd5 Qxd5 12. Nc3 Nxc3 13. bxc3 { [%cal Ga1b1,Gb1b5] } 13... Qd6 14. Rb1 b6 15. Re1 Be6 16. Bd3 { [%cal Ge6g4,Gg4d1] } 16... Rae8 (16... Bg4 17. h3 Bh5 18. Rb5 Bg6 { The pin can't be maintained anyway }) 17. Rb5 Na5 18. Rbe5 (18. Rh5 f5 (18... g6 19. Ng5 Bxg5 { [%cal Gh5h7] } 20. Rxg5 (20. Bxg5 gxh5 21. Qxh5 f5) (20. Rxh7 Kxh7 21. Qh5+ Kg7 22. Qxg5 $19)) 19. Bf4 Qxf4 20. Rxe6) 18... Nc6 19. R5e2 { [%csl Ge3] } 19... Bd7 20. d5 { [%cal Gc6e5,Gf3e5] } 20... Na5 (20... Qxd5 21. Bxh7+ $18) 21. Ne5 Bf6 { [%csl Ga5,Gd6] } 22. Bf4 { [%cal Gf4d6] } 22... Bxe5 23. Bxe5 Qxa3 24. Re3 { [%cal Ge3g3] } 24... Qc5 (24... g6 25. h4 { The attack would have continued with best play anyway. The queen AND knight are sidelined. }) 25. Bxh7+ Kxh7 26. Qh5+ { 1-0 Black resigns. } 26... Kg8 27. Bxg7 { [%cal Gh5h8] } 27... f5 (27... Kxg7 28. Rg3+ Kf6 29. Qg5#) 28. Qg6 { [%cal Gg7f6] } 28... Rf7 29. Rxe8+ Bxe8 30. Rxe8+ 1-0


