1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. Nd2 dxe4 { [%clk 0:02:51] } 4. Nxe4 Bf5 5. Ng3 Bg6 { [%clk 0:02:50] } 6. h4 h6 7. Nf3 { [%clk 0:03:05] } 7... Nd7 8. h5 Bh7 9. Bd3 Bxd3 10. Qxd3 Ngf6 11. Bd2 e6 12. O-O-O Bd6 13. Kb1 O-O { [%clk 0:02:46] } 14. Ne4 Nxe4 15. Qxe4 Nf6 16. Qe2 b5 17. g4! Nd5 18. g5 hxg5 19. Bxg5 Be7 20. Bd2 Bf6 { [%clk 0:01:59] } 21. Rdg1 Kh8 22. Qe4 Ne7! 23. c3?! { Clearly not an effective way to continue the attack. But I was low on time, and I couldn't see any concrete way to continue. } (23. Bg5!? Nf5 24. Bxf6 Qxf6 25. Ne5 Rad8) (23. Ng5!? Nf5) (23. Ne5 Qd5 24. Qg4 Bxe5 25. dxe5 Nf5 (25... Qxe5?? 26. Bc3! $18) 26. h6 g6 27. Rd1 $16) 23... Qd5 24. Qe2 c5 25. dxc5 Qxc5 26. Be3 (26. Bg5 Bxg5 27. Rxg5 Qc4 28. Qxc4 bxc4 29. h6 g6 30. Ra5 $16) 26... Qf5+ 27. Ka1 b4 28. Nd4 Qe4 29. f3?? (29. h6!! g6 30. Bg5! { [%cal Ge2e5,Gf6e5,Gg5e7] } 30... Qxe2 (30... Qe5 31. Qxe5 Bxe5 32. Bxe7) 31. Bxf6+ Kh7 32. Nxe2) 29... Qe5 $10 { Flagged. } 0-1


