ated since the queen controls the weakened light squares. }) 36. Qxa6 { [%clk 0:00:17] } (36. Qxg7#) 36... gxh6 { [%clk 0:00:03] } 37. Qxh6+ { [%clk 0:00:19] } 37... Kg8 { [%clk 0:00:05] } 38. Qg6+ { [%clk 0:00:19] } 38... Kf8 { [%clk 0:00:06] } 39. f4! { To further open up my king on the f file. } { [%clk 0:00:16] } 39... exf4 { [%clk 0:00:05] } 40. Rf1 { [%clk 0:00:17] } 40... Rd6 { [%clk 0:00:04] } 41. Rxf4+ { [%clk 0:00:16] } 41... Rf6 { [%clk 0:00:05] } 42. Nxf6 { [%clk 0:00:16] } 42... Bxf6 { [%clk 0:00:04] } 43. Rxf6+ { [%clk 0:00:18] } 43... Ke7 { [%clk 0:00:06] } 44. Qg7+ { [%clk 0:00:19] } 44... Ke8 { [%clk 0:00:06] } 45. Rf8# { 1-0 White wins by checkmate. } { [%clk 0:00:17] } 1-0


