1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 e6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 a6 5. c4 Qc7 6. Nc3 Nf6 7. Be3 Bb4 8. f3 O-O 9. Qd2 Nc6 10. Nc2 Be7 11. Be2 b6 12. a3 Bb7 13. O-O Ne5 14. b3 Bc5 15. Bxc5 Qxc5+ 16. Ne3 Rac8 17. b4 Qc6 18. Rac1 d6 19. Rfd1 Rfd8 20. Kh1 Qd7 21. Qa2 h6 22. Qb3 d5 23. cxd5 exd5 24. Ncxd5 Rxc1 25. Nxf6+ gxf6 26. Rxc1 Qd2 27. Rc2 (27. Rd1 Qxe2 28. Rxd8+ Kh7 29. h3 { Would have been enough to easily win, but I had 5 seconds left at this point. }) 27... Qe1+ 28. Bf1 Nd3 29. Qc4 Qxe3 { And I lost on time. } *


