1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 { [%cal Gb8c6,Gg8f6] } 2... Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 4. d3 a6 5. Ba4 (5. Bxc6 bxc6 6. Nxe5 d5 7. O-O dxe4 8. dxe4 Qxd1 9. Rxd1 Nxe4 10. Re1 f5 11. f3 Bc5+ 12. Be3 Bb4 (12... Bxe3+ 13. Rxe3 Nd6 14. Ng6+) 13. c3 Bd6 14. Nxc6 Kd7) 5... b5 6. Bb3 { [%cal Gc2c3,Gd3d4] } 6... Bb4+ 7. c3 Bc5 8. O-O O-O 9. d4 { [%cal Ge5d4,Gc3d4] } (9. Nxe5 Nxe5 10. d4 Bb7 11. dxc5 Nxe4) 9... Bb6 10. Re1 (10. Nxe5 Nxe4 (10... Nxe5 11. dxe5 Nxe4 12. Bd5 Nxf2 13. Rxf2 Bxf2+ 14. Kxf2 c6 15. Bb3 Qh4+ 16. Kg1 Re8 17. Nd2 d5 18. Nf3 Qe7 19. Bf4 Bg4 20. Qd4 Bxf3 21. gxf3 Qh4 22. Bg3 Qg5 23. f4 Qg4 24. Re1 Qg6 25. Qf2 f5 26. Kh1) 11. Bd5) 10... d6 { [%csl Ge4,Gd4,Gf4] } 11. h3 exd4 12. cxd4 Re8 { [%csl Ge4] } 13. Ng5?! (13. Nc3 b4 14. Nd5!! Nxe4?? 15. Nxb6 cxb6 16. Bd5! { [%csl Ge4,Gc6] }) 13... Re7 { [%csl Gd4,Ge4,Gb1,Gc1] } 14. d5 { [%csl Gc8][%cal Gc6d4,Gc6a5] } 14... h6 { [%csl Gc8,Gd8,Ga8] } (14... Nd4 15. Nc3 h6 16. Nf3 { The line I was most afraid of. }) 15. dxc6 hxg5 16. Bxg5 Qe8 { [%cal Ge8c6,Gg5d8] } 17. Nc3 { [%csl Gg5,Gc3,Ga1] } 17... Qxc6 { [%csl Gc8,Ga8][%cal Gg5f6] } 18. Qf3 { [%cal Gc8b7,Gc8e6] } (18. Bxf6 gxf6 19. Nd5 Re6 20. Rc1 Qe8 21. Qg4+ Kh8 22. Qh4+ Kg7 23. Rc3 { [%cal Gc3g3] }) 18... Ba5 { [%csl Gc8,Ga8] } (18... Bd4 19. Nd5 Nxd5 (19... Re6 20. Nxf6+ { [%cal Gb3d5] }) 20. Bxd5) 19. Bxf6 gxf6 20. Nd5!! { [%cal Gd5f6] } 20... Re6 (20... Bxe1?? 21. Nxe7+! { [%cal Ge7c6,Ge7g8] }) 21. Nxf6+ Kg7 (21... Rxf6?! 22. Qxf6 Be6 (22... Bxe1?? { [%csl Gc8,Ga8] } 23. Qxf7+ Kh8 24. Qg8# { [%cal Ga8g8] }) 23. Re3) 22. Bxe6 Bxe1?? (22... Bxe6 23. Rac1 Qb6 24. Nh5+ Kg6 25. Qf6+ { I was trying to evaluate this line, but couldn't see the mate beyond here. } 25... Kxh5 26. g4+ Bxg4 27. hxg4+ Kxg4 28. Qg7+ Kh5 29. Kg2) 23. Nh5+ Kg6 (23... Kh6 24. Qf6+ Kxh5 (24... Kh7 25. Qg7#) 25. g4#) 24. Qxf7+ Kg5 25. f4+ Kh6 (25... Kh4 26. Qf6+ Kxh5 27. Qg5#) 26. Qg7+ Kxh5 27. Qg5# { [%csl Gc8,Ga8] } *


